INSERT INTO `toons_ideas` VALUES(107, 'Skydiving', 'Skydiving Caricature Toons', '<h3 align="center">Welcome to our Skydiving Caricature Toons Gallery.</h3>', '<p align="justify">There is no other adventure in the world that matches the thrill of Skydiving! Some are very excited to jump given the chance, while others have panic attacks at the mention of skydiving.  It is a truly exhilarating experience to fall with the wind and reach out to touch the clouds. Have you recently had the life-changing experience of skydiving? And are you reluctant to show your frightened look in the photograph? Now that, you are puzzled on how to present this experience to your friends and family, we at caricaturetoons.com have a unique solution for you. A hilarious skydiving caricature is a perfect way to show-off your skydiving experience with a touch of humor! Just give us your prized photograph and a brief description of your experience. We will find a funny theme for your caricature, based on your experience.\r\nAre you stumped for a way to show your appreciation to the skydiving enthusiast among your friends? Just send in his/her photograph. We will make a caricature portraying him/her in action. Skydiving is indeed a high-adrenaline adventure. When your skydiver friend takes a look at this unique gift, he is surely going to have a great laugh and will surely treasure it for a long time to come.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="justify">Do you have a friend who is too scared and discouraged to go skydiving with you? You can cheer him up with a cute skydiving caricature toon showing him in a funny skydiving getup. These caricatures will help him to lighten up and be encouraged to join you for skydiving. We can include situations like, a surprised bird ogling at you during the free-fall, or a bird enjoying a piggy back ride on your parachute and many more. These themes will surely spread a smile on your face.\r\nOur artists are particularly attentive to details. You will be surprised to see the details they have taken into account while making the caricatures. They make toons that are rich in color and content. We think of an attractive background for your caricatures and include them to make them more attention-grabbing. They distort and exaggerate the face of the characters in the toon to make it more comical in appearance. The best thing about our caricatures is that, these are extremely flexible. Our caricatures maybe printed on various items like, T-shirts, mugs, water bottles, stickers and more.\r\nSo, don’t wait to think twice about ordering caricatures from caricaturetoons.com. These make excellent gifts to your near and dear ones. Just visit the site and order a caricature today!</p>\r\n\r\n', '', '', ' ');
