INSERT INTO `toon_messages` VALUES(763, 318, 1434, 'Hi sir, firstly i hope it’s not too much  to request  clearer pictures of the two of you, the one you attached are  blurry and low resolution and the face details are quite hard to recognize..hope it’s ok....secondly about the mario pictures you send, i didnt get the bowser’s castle so i googled it, so i can have an idea of what you are describing,can you send the one you have so i know we have the same pictures?\r\nYour idea is great but here are some concerns with regards to your concept....\r\n1.The idea where the princess is atop a castle and mario is climbing while throwing a ball of fire to bowser is good but to achieve this i need a bigger “portion” of the castle to put the characters on...meaning if you want to capture the whole castle and the background , the lava ,sky,lightning,etc..  this “portion” of the castle will become smaller too, hence the character will likely become smaller too...in order to portray mario climbing while the princess is on the tower only a portion of the wall of the castle will be shown...\r\n2.The background is a rendered drawing which took a very long time for the artist to draw and render, and it will take very long to recreate a similiar essence of this drawing...i can make a simplier version(using my style of course) of this but not as intricate as the one in the drawing....\r\nHere are my suggestions...\r\nIf you want, i will use the original drawing of bowsers castle as a bacgkround, then i will just put this scene in front ,the princess is already riding atop yoshi on the right side while mario is in the middle fighting bowser with his ball of fire, and i’ll just add dry bones somewhere in the picture \r\nOr...Well go on with your original idea except for the whole original bowser castle background, and ill just make the necessary rendition of the castle that will go along with the scene....\r\nLet me know what you think, tnx\r\n\r\nRodel', '', 1, '2012-12-11 01:57:56');
