INSERT INTO `toon_static` VALUES(2, 'PAGE_AFFILIATES', 'Affiliates', '', '<p>EARN EXTRA CASH!!! </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Become a Caricature Toons Affiliate and promote our caricatures and artists on your website or blog. We have various caricaturist artists that can satisfy any taste.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>All you need to do is place an ad or link on your site and direct them to us. For every order placed through your referal you earn a 15% commission. It&rsquo;s a great way to put some bucks in your pocket and direct people to a great website.</p><p><br />It&rsquo;s FREE TO JOIN and EARN MONEY on Caricature Toons or merchandise purchased through our site.&nbsp;</p><p><br />We provide you with various sized banner ads and links and very generous payouts. We also provide you with online access to view your commissions earned and even pay monthly.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It&rsquo;s FREE to sign up and EASY to get started.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>');
INSERT INTO `toon_static` VALUES(3, 'PAGE_FAQS', 'Faq''s', '', '<div class="static_text_heading" align="center" style="padding-bottom: 30px; padding-top: 20px">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</div><!--StartFragment-->  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>How Long does it take to get my Caricature Toon? </span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">Each Caricaturists style is different, and so are their turnaround times. In the &ldquo;Styles and Prices&rdquo; section, under the Artist pricing, it shows the length of time that you can expect to receive the first proof of your Caricature Toon. The days are calculated as Calendar days. If you require any alterations or adjustments, this will add to the overall turnaround time. Your Caricaturist will gladly let you know when your revised Caricatures will be ready.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>How many changes can I make?</span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">You can make as many tweaks as you like if your Caricature Toon is not to your original specifications. Sending new images or revising instructions after your first proof will require additional charges. If it is dramatically different, we may ask you to place a new order.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>How does the 100% Money Back Guarantee work?</span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">Simple, if your not 100% satisfied with the final result (based on no changes to your original instructions) and have given the Artist ample opportunity to make it right, we will refund your money. No questions asked.&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>Can I change Artist Styles after I&rsquo;ve placed an order?</span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span>No,<span style="color: #123e8f"> </span><span style="color: #044ba2">unless your Caricature Toon has not yet been started by the Artist. If it has been started, which typically happens within the first 24 hours, you cannot change Artists without placing and paying for a new order. Each Artist is an independent freelancer and you are committed to their style once an order has been placed.</span></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>What resolution and sizes are the final files? </span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">They are an 8 x 10&nbsp;at a 300 dpi resolution or 2400 x 3000 pixels.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>Are my Caricature Toon&rsquo;s Royalty Free?</span></strong><span> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">Yes, you own them out-right and can do whatever you like with your caricatures. We do however reserve the right to use your Caricature Toon in any of our Marketing and Promotional materials.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>Will you do non-</span></strong><strong><span>caricature</span></strong><strong><span> themed Caricature Toons?</span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">Yes, absolutely. Just follow the same ordering process and tell us your non-</span><span style="color: #044ba2">caricature</span><span style="color: #044ba2"> caricature toon vision.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>What is your information privacy policy?</span></strong><span> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">We do not share or sell your personal information or email address with anyone. From time to time we may send you information or special offers, however, if you prefer not to receive them, you can easily unsubscribe at any time.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>Can I cancel my Caricature Toon order?</span></strong><span> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">Yes, providing we haven&rsquo;t started your caricature. If we&rsquo;ve already started, which is typically 24 hours after we receive your order we do not provide refunds.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>Can I cancel my Products or Merchandise order?</span></strong><span> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">No, unfortunately not. Our manufacturing facility uses automation to produce your order immediately. Once the order is placed it is produced shortly thereafter.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>Do you have the same 100% money back Guarantee on the Products or Merchandise?</span></strong><span> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">No, but we offer a 100% Satisfaction Guarantee. If it is lost or damaged in shipping, or has any workmanship defects, we will replace it. All we ask is that you report any problems to us within 48 hours of accepting shipment. We may require you to ship the product back at our expense or provide a digital photograph of the defect.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>How much is Shipping?</span></strong><span style="color: #123e8f"> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">For Caricature Toons there is no shipping fees, all Caricatures are free downloads through our website. For Products and Merchandise, shipping is calculated at check out and is based on weight, destination and shipping method.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>How long does it take to get Caricature Toons Products or Merchandise?</span></strong><span> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">Once we receive your orders it typically takes 3 - 5 days to manufacture. Depending on the method of shipping you choose, it will take an additional 1- 14 days business days of shipping time.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>Who do I contact to follow up on my order?</span></strong><span> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">Just drop us an email at </span><a href="mailto:toonhelper@triathlontoons.com"><span>toonhelper@caricaturetoons.com</span></a><span style="color: #044ba2"> and we&rsquo;ll get back to you, usually the same day. </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>Will you ship World Wide?<span style="color: #123e8f"> </span></span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">Yes, we do it all the time.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>What is your Copyright Infringement Policy? </span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">We assume all materials you provide to us you have permission to use. We do not accept any responsibility for copyright infringement for reproducing any of the materials you supplied to us.&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #123e8f">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span>Can you add text as part of my Caricature Toon?</span></strong></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">Yes, absolutely, many of our caricatures have text included. Just tell us what you want and where you want it as part of your instructions. </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="color: #044ba2">What are the characteristics of the best images to send?</span></strong><span style="color: #044ba2"> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">For faces, the ideal photograph is a straight on shot with the facial expression that is closest to what you&rsquo;d like to see. Think of a head and shoulders &ldquo;Passport Style&rdquo; photograph. It is also helpful to supply a second photograph showing a &ldquo;Three Quarter Head Shot&rdquo;. This is a shot with a slight turn of the head showing the side profile and most all of the front of the face. If the photo&rsquo;s you supplied are not ideal, your Caricaturist will contact you and let you know. </span>For the body, props or backgrounds you can supply images or describe in detail what you&rsquo;d like to see. Many of our customers find images or links off the Internet and send them to us to use as an example of what they are trying to describe. </p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="color: #044ba2">How do I get in contact with the Artist who is creating my Caricature Toons?</span></strong><span style="color: #044ba2"> That&rsquo;s easy, just go to our website and in the My Toons section you will see a &ldquo;Talk to My Toonist&rdquo; link. After you&rsquo;ve clicked that link you will see an orange envelope, click on that, and you will see an Instant Messaging box where you can send a message and even upload new images if required.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="color: #044ba2">How will I know if my Artist has questions for me?</span></strong><span style="color: #044ba2"> </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #044ba2">No sweat, you will receive an email message. You then reply through the &ldquo;My Toons&rdquo; section of the website. You can also check your &ldquo;My Toons&rdquo; section under &ldquo;view communications&rdquo; and if you see a Green Envelope it means you have an unread message. When you click on the envelope a message box will appear.</span></p>  <!--EndFragment-->   <div align="center" style="padding-bottom: 20px">&nbsp;</div><div align="center" style="padding-bottom: 20px">&nbsp;</div><div align="center" style="padding-bottom: 20px">&nbsp;</div>  <!--EndFragment-->   ');
