INSERT INTO `toon_static` VALUES(5, 'PAGE_ARTAPP', 'Artist Application Page', '', '<div class="static_text_heading" align="center" style="padding-bottom: 30px; padding-top: 20px">ARTIST APPLICATION PAGE</div><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>About our Program</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal">At Caricature Toons we are fast becoming one of the largest and most  trusted online caricature ordering sites on the web. A big part of what  makes us successful is that we offer many different styles of  caricatures. Our caricature artists are located all over the World and  each has a unique perspective. We like to say, &ldquo;We have a stroke for  every kind of folk&rdquo;.<br /> <br /> We are constantly on the look out for great caricature artists to join  our team. We want our customer to be able to find a perfect caricature  style. More often than not caricatures are presented as special gifts  and end up becoming keepsakes, heck, who throws away a caricature of  themselves? Our Mission is to make sure we provide them with the perfect  style caricature, whatever their special occasion.<br /> <br /> What makes Caricature Toons different is our artists only have to do  what they do best, and that&rsquo;s create great looking caricatures that  bring smiles to people faces that create memories. At caricature toons  we take care of all the marketing, and we do a lot of it. There is no  need for you to build a website, set up payment gateways&nbsp;and try to market yourself. We do all that for you. We want you to focus  creating caricatures and putting smiles on people&rsquo;s faces and we&rsquo;ll  take care of the rest.<br /> <br /> If we think your style would be a hit on our site and we accept you as  an artist, you have great flexibility. Think of it as operating your own  business storefront on the web, except you don&rsquo;t have to worry about  payment administration, customer service, or marketing. We take care of  that.<br /> <br /> You are given access to your own artist dashboard where you can upload  yourgallery and within our guidelines set your prices and turnaround  times. If you&rsquo;re slow, you are given the ability to lower your pricing  or reduce your turnaround time. If you get too busy, or want to take  that vacation, no problem, you can turn off your gallery at anytime.  When you&rsquo;re ready to get back to work you simply turn it on and your  back in the business of making great looking caricature gifts.<br /> <br /> We even have an easy job tracker in the Artist Administration dashboard.  At a moment&rsquo;s notice you can tell where every job is, does it need to  be started? When is it due? Is it waiting for customer approval? When  it&rsquo;s accepted and downloaded by the customer you know right away and it  even keeps track of your payments. In the dashboard you also have easy  upload features and the entire customer interaction process is  automated. No need to email back and forth between the customers with  misplaced instructions and images. Our artists tell us they love working  with us, we&nbsp;make their job easier. We love what they do by drawing great looking caricatures, it&rsquo;s the ideal partnering relationship.<br /> <br /> Applying is easy. Simply fill out the application form on this page,  upload your sample images and apply. We will review the images and get  back to you. Be sure to upload Caricatures image samples only. The  number one reason we turn down artists is because their style is not  caricature art. They may be great painters or illustrators but didn&rsquo;t  supply us with great looking caricatures. So it&rsquo;s very important you  only upload caricature samples<br /> <br /> If your caricature style is accepted we&rsquo;ll be in contact with our  pricing, turnaround, quality and business requirements. If you agree the  next step is to set up your public gallery with before and after shots.  We&rsquo;ll then turn you on your gallery. It&rsquo;s important to note we can&rsquo;t  guarantee volume of business and our most asked question is &ldquo;how busy  will I be? Will I get a lot of work?&rdquo; Great questions, unfortunately we  can&rsquo;t answer that, it all depends on the customer&rsquo;s selection and what  style, turnaround and price point they are looking for. We will say that  some caricature artists are very busy. But it all depends.<br /> <br /> If you think you have what it takes and want to do what you do best,  draw caricatures, then please apply. We&rsquo;d love to see your work. If you  have any questions please feel free to contact us.</p><div>&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><p>&nbsp;</p>');
